OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,FFour British people have died within
OL,7,Ffour months after being struck down
OL,8,Fwith stomach bugs while on holiday in
OL,9,FCape Verde, lawyers representing their
OL,10,Ffamilies have said.
OL,12,FKaren Pooley, 64, from
OL,13,FGloucestershire, Elena Walsh, 64, from
OL,14,FBirmingham, Mark Ashley, 55, of
OL,15,FBedfordshire, and a 56-year-old man
OL,16,Fall died last year after contracting
OL,17,Fsevere gastric illnesses while on the
OL,18,Fislands off the coast of west Africa.
