OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,FThey are four of six Britons who have
OL,7,Fdied after holidays there since
OL,8,FJanuary 2023, and law firm Irwin
OL,9,FMitchell said investigations into the
OL,10,Fdeaths are "ongoing".
OL,12,FMs Pooley, from Lydney, travelled with
OL,13,Fa friend to the Riu Funana resort in
OL,14,FSal on October 7, 2025 for a
OL,15,Ffortnight's holiday costing #3,000 and
OL,16,Fbooked through Tui, the law firm said.
