OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,FThe retired mother-of-two became sick
OL,7,Fon October 11 with gastric symptoms
OL,8,Fincluding diarrhoea, and in the early
OL,9,Fhours of the next day she slipped on
OL,10,Fwater leaking from a fridge while
OL,11,Fgoing to the bathroom.
OL,13,FShe was transferred to a local clinic
OL,14,Fand over the next four days Ms Pooley
OL,15,Fcontinued to experience diarrhoea and
OL,16,Fvomiting, alongside severe pain from
OL,17,Fher fractured femur.
