OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,FThe 64-year-old was airlifted to
OL,7,FTenerife for urgent care on October 16
OL,8,Fand died in the early hours of the
OL,9,Fnext day, lawyers said.
OL,11,FHer husband Andy, 62, said: "We're
OL,12,Futterly heartbroken. Karen was the
OL,13,Fkindest, loveliest person.
OL,15,F"She was a devoted wife and mum who
OL,16,Floved swimming, walking the dog in the
OL,17,FForest of Dean, and volunteered at a
OL,18,Flocal charity shop. She was also a
OL,19,Fwonderful friend who lit up every room
OL,20,Fshe entered."
