OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,FJatinder Paul, serious injury lawyer
OL,7,Fat the firm, said: "The number of
OL,8,Fholidaymakers to Cape Verde being
OL,9,Fstruck down with serious and
OL,10,Fdebilitating gastric illnesses is
OL,11,Ftruly staggering. Nothing brings the
OL,12,Fgravity of this situation into sharper
OL,13,Ffocus than these recent deaths.
OL,15,F"In my experience I'm used to
OL,16,Fsupporting holidaymakers who have
OL,17,Ffallen ill at resorts across the
OL,18,Fglobe, but I've never seen repeated
OL,19,Fand continued illness outbreaks at the
OL,20,Fsame resorts on such a scale over such
OL,21,Fa period of time.
OL,26,@oD@TOUwD@AOU
