OL,3,CLydney woman is among four dead after
OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,F"It's almost incomprehensible that
OL,7,Fholidaymakers continue to describe the
OL,8,Fhygiene issues at these Cape Verde
OL,9,Fhotels year-after-year. Each case
OL,10,Fisn't a statistic; it's a human story
OL,11,Fof how lives have been turned upside
OL,12,Fdown.
OL,14,F"Understandably, those we represent
OL,15,Fhave serious concerns about hygiene
OL,16,Fstandards in Cape Verde. While nothing
OL,17,Fcan make up for what's happened, we're
OL,18,Fdetermined to at least help establish
OL,19,Fthe answers they deserve.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
