OL,4,CCape Verde stomach bugs, law firm says
OL,6,F"In the meantime, we call for
OL,7,Fmeaningful and decisive action to get
OL,8,Fon top of the reported hygiene issues
OL,9,Fon the islands. Tour operators are
OL,10,Fresponsible for ensuring the safety of
OL,11,Fthose who have booked all-inclusive
OL,12,Fpackage holidays. Therefore, we urge
OL,13,Fthem to work with the authorities to
OL,14,Fensure the highest hygiene and safety
OL,15,Fstandards are always upheld."
OL,17,FTui has been contacted for comment.
